---
title: Walnut-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Caramelised Apple Chutney & Cheesy Hasselback Potatoes
description: A five-star dinner doesn’t need need to take hours to prepare and you certainly don’t need to be a renowned chef either to pull
this dish off. Roasted potatoes are spruced up by baking a layer of sharp Parmesan on top and this pork is getting the ultimate
treatment by dressing it in a walnut crust. A luxurious dinner without the trouble.
